            <title>[LU-1049] lc_net does not parse unexpected output from pdsh well</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1049</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Attachment 30730 of Oracle bugzilla 23234 was landed in b1_8 and master tree and was picked up into Whamcloud git trees.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, comment#18 of the bugzilla showed the fix was flawed. Attachment 32953 contains the correct fix that worked for us. We thus need to carry a local patch. Please pick up this fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
